Update an MSE object with new slots

Updates an existing MSE object (class MSE) from a previous version of the DLMtool to include the new slots. The slots will be empty, but avoids the 'slot doesn't exist' error that sometimes occurs.

updateMSE(MSEobj)

Arguments

MSEobj

A MSE object from a previous version of the DLMtool

Value

An object of class MSE
